05:49.000 --> 05:51.000
We have not have progressed where we're at.

05:51.000 --> 05:53.000
He, it is because of him that we've arrived here.

05:53.000 --> 05:54.000
Sounds like a genius.

05:54.000 --> 05:56.000
Sounds like a cool guy to hang out with.

05:56.000 --> 05:57.000
Oh, yeah.

05:57.000 --> 05:58.000
He's a very, very cool dude.

05:58.000 --> 06:01.000
And the other one is Mr. D.

06:01.000 --> 06:04.000
