06:04.000 --> 06:07.000
So, for a while, we couldn't detect the UAPs with radar.

06:07.000 --> 06:11.000
Actually, the radar was detecting them, but not telling us it was detecting them.

06:11.000 --> 06:19.000
And Mr. D figured out, hey, we can detect signals from these craft and geolocate them or direction find them in the sky.

06:19.000 --> 06:21.000
