11:07.000 --> 11:16.000
A drone, a drone of the same size in the same flight formation would have been blaringly obvious, glaringly obvious, excuse me.

11:16.000 --> 11:18.000
So it would have been so obvious that we couldn't have missed it.

11:18.000 --> 11:21.000
So UAP, by definition, is, you know, unidentified.

11:21.000 --> 11:22.000
Yeah.

11:22.000 --> 11:26.000
