11:36.000 --> 11:47.000
that's probably Russian or Chinese, because there's a lot of reasons for them to want to see, you know, the red team, blue team stuff that we're doing at home here in the U.S., right?

11:47.000 --> 11:51.000
Or is your first instinct, this is not, this is not from here?

11:51.000 --> 11:54.000
