12:01.000 --> 12:02.000
Uh-huh.

12:02.000 --> 12:03.000
It doesn't make any sense.

12:03.000 --> 12:11.000
I've been on project and had special programs without telling us bring their secret things to our event.

12:11.000 --> 12:12.000
Uh-huh.

12:12.000 --> 12:20.000
