12:20.000 --> 12:21.000
Yeah.

12:21.000 --> 12:23.000
They're going to tell your interns that don't know, have a clearance, don't know anything.

12:23.000 --> 12:24.000
Yeah.

12:24.000 --> 12:26.000
And we're just going to write it off and move on.

12:26.000 --> 12:27.000
Right.

12:27.000 --> 12:28.000
Right.

12:28.000 --> 12:38.000
