13:02.000 --> 13:03.000
Interesting.

13:03.000 --> 13:04.000
Right.

13:04.000 --> 13:13.000
And I would also offer that what we are seeing, my observations and my team's observations are that whoever or whatever is controlling these is probing our capabilities.

13:13.000 --> 13:22.000
So, it's not like if I see a class one, it doesn't just stay in a straight azimuth and fly north to south like it was already flying.

13:22.000 --> 13:23.000
Okay.

