49:00.000 --> 49:17.000
So I think we have reached the point where our government has decided that it needs to release knowledge about the advanced physics and science, but at the same time needs to constrain that Lockheed engineer or scientist from revealing our national secrets and protecting our national defense.

49:17.000 --> 49:24.000
