01:39:05.620 --> 01:39:07.620
Uh, one unit of measure of the craft.

01:39:07.620 --> 01:39:08.620
Uh huh.

01:39:08.620 --> 01:39:09.620
To the left and to the right.

01:39:09.620 --> 01:39:10.620
Really it's one vibrating.

01:39:10.620 --> 01:39:13.620
And you know that because it comes out of the, out of the oscillation.

01:39:13.620 --> 01:39:14.620
Uh huh.

01:39:14.620 --> 01:39:15.620
And stops.

01:39:15.620 --> 01:39:16.620
Uh huh.

01:39:16.620 --> 01:39:21.620
And it'll turn it back on and it moves so fast that our system thinks it's a propeller.

01:39:21.620 --> 01:39:22.620
Uh huh.

01:39:22.620 --> 01:39:25.620
So when it, when it oscillates as a propeller, it thinks, interprets it as.

01:39:25.620 --> 01:39:26.620
Uh huh.

01:39:26.620 --> 01:39:31.620
And then it'll stop oscillating and then just kind of keep, continue flying and then the

01:39:31.620 --> 01:39:33.620
radar will indicate that it's not a propeller anymore.

01:39:33.620 --> 01:39:34.620
Wow.

01:39:34.620 --> 01:39:35.620
Right.

01:39:35.620 --> 01:39:37.620
So, um, it does change brightness.

01:39:37.620 --> 01:39:38.620
Uh huh.

01:39:38.620 --> 01:39:42.620
It'll seem to like get very energetic, much like the class three blob does.

01:39:42.620 --> 01:39:43.620
Uh huh.

01:39:43.620 --> 01:39:48.620
It'll, it'll emanate more light as it vibrates really fast.

01:39:48.620 --> 01:39:52.620
And then when the light kind of dies down, it stops vibrating as fast until it stops vibrating

01:39:52.620 --> 01:39:53.620
completely.

01:39:53.620 --> 01:39:54.620
Uh huh.

01:39:54.620 --> 01:39:56.620
And then it'll go back almost like a cycle.

01:39:56.620 --> 01:40:01.620
Almost like somebody starting a process and that process, um, that chain continues until

01:40:01.620 --> 01:40:03.620
it's exhausted and then it returns to its old state.

01:40:03.620 --> 01:40:04.620
Uh huh.

01:40:04.620 --> 01:40:07.620
And that's kind of what the impression is of what we're seeing with the class six.

01:40:07.620 --> 01:40:08.620
Fascinating.

01:40:12.620 --> 01:40:14.620
Class eight is the Hornet.

01:40:14.620 --> 01:40:15.620
Okay.

01:40:15.620 --> 01:40:17.620
Um, we've only seen a class eight a couple of times.

01:40:17.620 --> 01:40:18.620
Interesting.

01:40:18.620 --> 01:40:19.620
Yep.

01:40:19.620 --> 01:40:20.620
Um, kind of like the class five, it's kind of elusive.

01:40:20.620 --> 01:40:21.620
Yeah.

01:40:21.620 --> 01:40:22.620
We've seen a whole bunch.

01:40:22.620 --> 01:40:23.620
Um.

01:40:23.620 --> 01:40:29.620
Anything specific that you did around that time where the, the, the Hornet entered or.

