We just couldn't.

01:41:11.620 --> 01:41:12.620
Wow.

01:41:12.620 --> 01:41:13.620
Couldn't ever see it.

01:41:13.620 --> 01:41:14.620
Class nine.

01:41:14.620 --> 01:41:15.620
Uh, the class nine is the egg.

01:41:15.620 --> 01:41:16.620
That's the egg.

01:41:16.620 --> 01:41:18.620
So is this is so fascinating.

01:41:18.620 --> 01:41:19.620
Is this the hope?

01:41:19.620 --> 01:41:25.620
Because I, you know, I spoke to Jake, I think it was in January and we had a really interesting

01:41:25.620 --> 01:41:26.620
discussion.

01:41:26.620 --> 01:41:28.620
He said, he expressed, he exuded a lot of confidence.

01:41:28.620 --> 01:41:32.620
He said in six months, we're going to get this thing to land.

01:41:32.620 --> 01:41:39.620
If all things go well before, I'm trying not to say a date, but within the first half

01:41:39.620 --> 01:41:46.620
of 2025, we hope to do a demonstration and, and invite key members of the public from institutions,

01:41:46.620 --> 01:41:50.620
um, and demonstrate this and maybe even get something to the ground.

01:41:50.620 --> 01:41:52.620
And that's going to answer a lot of questions.

01:41:52.620 --> 01:41:56.620
That would be absolutely insane.

01:41:56.620 --> 01:42:00.620
And I don't know, maybe that's a, you know, Elon Musk style timeline.

01:42:00.620 --> 01:42:06.620
That's a little aggressive or something, but is it, can you guys get the egg to land?

01:42:06.620 --> 01:42:11.620
Is that presumably, I would assume that's the hope because of his past experience.

01:42:11.620 --> 01:42:17.620
I look at some of these other classes and to me, there's such a gap between like the,

01:42:17.620 --> 01:42:20.620
I don't know, the manta ray or hornet or some of these things.

01:42:20.620 --> 01:42:26.620
And like, you know, a concrete object, like on the ground that you can like reverse engineer

01:42:26.620 --> 01:42:27.620
and fly.

01:42:27.620 --> 01:42:31.620
So is the hope the egg and can you guys bring it down pretty, pretty quickly, you know,

01:42:31.620 --> 01:42:33.620
through peaceful psionic means or.

01:42:33.620 --> 01:42:34.620
I have no expectation.

01:42:34.620 --> 01:42:35.620
Okay.

01:42:35.620 --> 01:42:36.620
I literally don't know.

01:42:36.620 --> 01:42:37.620
Yeah.

01:42:37.620 --> 01:42:38.620
Like is the egg a real craft?

01:42:38.620 --> 01:42:39.620
Yeah.

01:42:39.620 --> 01:42:44.620
Is the thing we imaged with our rudimentary imaging system at the time, even there.

01:42:44.620 --> 01:42:45.620
Right.

01:42:45.620 --> 01:42:49.620
Um, if it is there, can Jordan or someone else control it?

01:42:49.620 --> 01:42:50.620
Right.

01:42:50.620 --> 01:42:53.620
If they can't control it, are they able to tell it to land and have it land?

