01:49:32.620 --> 01:49:34.620
What, uh, what's your take on the Jersey drone situation?

01:49:34.620 --> 01:49:38.620
We were, we were just talking about that before we started rolling and it still feels

01:49:38.620 --> 01:49:40.620
so frustratingly inconclusive.

01:49:40.620 --> 01:49:46.620
You have the White House saying that they were FAA research drones after Trump, I think,

01:49:46.620 --> 01:49:48.620
told his, you know, special assistant, go look into this.

01:49:48.620 --> 01:49:53.620
And that was just such an unsatisfying answer for so many, you know, residents of Jersey.

01:49:53.620 --> 01:49:56.620
Um, what, what, what do you think was happening?

01:49:56.620 --> 01:50:03.620
I think, um, one of our adversaries has the ability to fly with impunity and operate in

01:50:03.620 --> 01:50:06.620
our airspace and we are helpless to stop it.

01:50:06.620 --> 01:50:07.620
That's insane.

01:50:07.620 --> 01:50:09.620
That's really scary.

01:50:09.620 --> 01:50:15.620
Um, and, uh, any reason to believe that, that you can discuss publicly or?

01:50:15.620 --> 01:50:21.620
Uh, I, I think that, uh, Langley air force base based on, uh, news articles was probably

01:50:21.620 --> 01:50:28.620
done by China and, um, that was 17 days of just completely unperturbed incursion.

01:50:28.620 --> 01:50:29.620
Yes, exactly.

01:50:29.620 --> 01:50:34.620
And, and I think that, uh, you know, we know that the HAB, uh, the balloon that flew through

01:50:34.620 --> 01:50:35.620
was from China.

01:50:35.620 --> 01:50:41.620
Um, so there's only one entity that has a past performance to my knowledge of flying in our

01:50:41.620 --> 01:50:45.620
airspace with apparent impunity, uh, with us not doing anything to stop it.

01:50:45.620 --> 01:50:46.620
And that's China.

01:50:46.620 --> 01:50:47.620
Okay.

01:50:47.620 --> 01:50:52.620
So why wouldn't you naturally arrive at a sustained, uh, intrusion in our airspace?

01:50:52.620 --> 01:50:55.620
Why wouldn't you assume it's China until proven otherwise?

01:50:55.620 --> 01:51:00.620
If you have two explicit examples of very high likelihood being China, or we know it's

01:51:00.620 --> 01:51:01.620
China.

01:51:01.620 --> 01:51:07.620
So the question we have to ask ourselves is, are the craft we're seeing group three drones?

01:51:07.620 --> 01:51:13.620
Are they UAPs operated by China and, and what are the permutations thereof?

01:51:13.620 --> 01:51:16.620
Like, what does it mean if it is or isn't a UAP?

01:51:16.620 --> 01:51:19.620
Can they carry payloads if they're flying with exotic flight principles?

01:51:19.620 --> 01:51:22.620
I mean, that's a really scary possibility.

01:51:22.620 --> 01:51:24.620
And what is the purpose?

01:51:24.620 --> 01:51:29.620
If, if it is a China or a Russia or whoever it is, to what end?

01:51:29.620 --> 01:51:32.620
Why would they do that to the American populace?

01:51:32.620 --> 01:51:35.620
Why would they continue when they know we're looking?

01:51:35.620 --> 01:51:37.620
Is it to show our incompetence?

01:51:37.620 --> 01:51:42.120
Is it, is it to derail our national security apparatus and say like, look how incompetent

01:51:42.120 --> 01:51:43.120
you are.

01:51:43.120 --> 01:51:44.120
We can do what we want.

01:51:44.120 --> 01:51:45.120
Is it because-

01:51:45.120 --> 01:51:47.120
That's why I have trouble believing it's China, right?

01:51:47.120 --> 01:51:48.120
Yeah.

01:51:48.120 --> 01:51:50.120
It's just so, I mean, what a flex, right?

01:51:50.120 --> 01:51:54.360
Like if you're doing that over residential neighborhoods in Jersey, that's kind of an act

01:51:54.360 --> 01:51:55.360
of war.

01:51:55.360 --> 01:51:56.360
That's serious.

01:51:56.360 --> 01:51:59.820
I think that's why our government's constrained, right?

01:51:59.820 --> 01:52:06.320
Because on the one hand, our government whose job is to protect the nation can't come out

01:52:06.320 --> 01:52:07.320
and be incompetent.

01:52:07.320 --> 01:52:08.320
No.

01:52:08.320 --> 01:52:09.320
Like it cannot be done.

01:52:09.320 --> 01:52:10.320
Totally.

01:52:10.320 --> 01:52:11.320
Like they have to be able to protect us.

01:52:11.320 --> 01:52:18.320
I think in the 60 minutes article or episode they did on this, they spoke with the NORAD

01:52:18.320 --> 01:52:19.320
commander.

01:52:19.320 --> 01:52:21.520
And he said something that was very telling.

01:52:21.520 --> 01:52:27.920
He said that, um, uh, we have allowed, uh, technology, uh, the threat to grow.

01:52:27.920 --> 01:52:32.040
We don't have technology to match something, something along those lines, basically meaning

01:52:32.040 --> 01:52:40.320
that maybe whoever is doing this has a capability that we have not, uh, grown defensive technology

01:52:40.320 --> 01:52:41.320
enough to counter.

01:52:41.320 --> 01:52:42.320
That's freaky.

01:52:42.320 --> 01:52:47.080
Well, then you have the Trump statement at the time where he goes, uh, Biden knows what,

01:52:47.080 --> 01:52:48.840
you know, they know what this is.

01:52:48.840 --> 01:52:50.200
