01:53:03.220 --> 01:53:07.460
I can't imagine it's the enemy because it was the enemy that blasted out.

01:53:07.460 --> 01:53:11.000
Even if they were late, they'd blast it.

01:53:11.000 --> 01:53:12.760
Anything strange is going on for some reason.

01:53:12.760 --> 01:53:14.680
They don't want to tell the people and they should.

01:53:14.680 --> 01:53:18.200
And then you had that, I think, sheriff, the local sheriff in New Jersey saying that

01:53:18.200 --> 01:53:22.940
he thought he saw them come out of the water and, you know, trans medium is this, you know,

01:53:22.940 --> 01:53:27.880
important observable of UAPs and, uh, you know, there are rumors of underwater bases and

01:53:27.880 --> 01:53:28.960
that sort of thing.

01:53:28.960 --> 01:53:34.880
So that made me think maybe NHI, but it's, I mean, it's also, I would talk about this with

01:53:34.880 --> 01:53:35.880
Jake.

01:53:35.880 --> 01:53:43.920
You know, you could use the presence of NHI, UAP to opportunistically flood the zone.

01:53:43.920 --> 01:53:46.080
And then it's extremely hard to figure out what's what.

01:53:46.080 --> 01:53:47.080
Yeah.

01:53:47.080 --> 01:53:48.080
I think so.

01:53:48.080 --> 01:53:49.640
I'm open to all concepts here.

01:53:49.640 --> 01:53:50.640
Mm-hmm.

01:53:50.640 --> 01:53:54.640
I personally, my opinion is that it's probably unnecessary and it's probably China.

01:53:54.640 --> 01:53:55.640
Yeah.

01:53:55.640 --> 01:54:01.840
But, um, that's why there's so many unknowns, like, like, um, how, how do you figure it out

01:54:01.840 --> 01:54:02.900
and tell the tale?

01:54:02.900 --> 01:54:08.640
I hope at the highest level we've figured it out, whether it's adversary or NHI, I hope,

01:54:08.720 --> 01:54:09.940
I hope somebody knows.

01:54:10.120 --> 01:54:11.060
Cause yeah.

01:54:11.160 --> 01:54:11.560
Yeah.

01:54:11.720 --> 01:54:13.220
I hope, I hope they do too.

01:54:13.300 --> 01:54:16.560
I like to have faith in my government and believe that they are doing the right thing.

01:54:16.800 --> 01:54:18.780
I know I was in the government for a long time.

01:54:18.780 --> 01:54:24.860
I know a lot of government officials, um, generally very, very good people, patriots

01:54:24.860 --> 01:54:27.740
who love their country and want nothing but the best for all of us.

01:54:27.740 --> 01:54:33.600
So I hope, I really hope that they do have this figured out and that they have a capability

01:54:33.600 --> 01:54:36.440
and that we can rest easy and not worry about it.

01:54:36.640 --> 01:54:39.420
But there's the potential that some of that might not be the case.

01:54:39.540 --> 01:54:39.700
Yeah.

01:54:39.740 --> 01:54:41.160
That maybe they haven't figured it out.

01:54:41.860 --> 01:54:47.740
And five years from today, do you have any hopes, dreams, expectations for skywatching?

01:54:47.740 --> 01:54:51.040
Yeah, I would like to have Skywatcher as part of the Golden Dome.

01:54:51.520 --> 01:54:54.740
I would like to be proactive on the UAP problem.

01:54:55.240 --> 01:54:57.800
We have a technology to detect UAPs.

01:54:58.400 --> 01:54:59.720
We're growing that technology.

01:55:00.260 --> 01:55:01.780
That technology should be everywhere.

01:55:02.760 --> 01:55:05.300
Not cause I'm a capitalist and want to make a lot of money.

01:55:05.420 --> 01:55:09.660
Of course, of course, most people want to make money and be independently wealthy.

01:55:10.200 --> 01:55:14.420
But for the national security implications of here's a phenomena, here's a thing on our

01:55:14.420 --> 01:55:19.700
airspace, moving with impunity through our air corridors and nobody knows anything about

01:55:19.700 --> 01:55:19.900
it.

01:55:20.300 --> 01:55:25.200
So if we deploy the right sensors in the right mix, we can become masters of our airspace

01:55:25.200 --> 01:55:28.260
and become air aware, if you will, of what's going on.

01:55:28.780 --> 01:55:30.840
So that's why we started Skywatcher.

01:55:30.920 --> 01:55:32.300
That's why we're developing the technology.

01:55:32.300 --> 01:55:35.060
And in five years, it'd be wonderful if it's deployed.

01:55:35.520 --> 01:55:41.600
And then now we can have a body of knowledge and data on this phenomena, on this threat,

01:55:41.800 --> 01:55:46.740
on this instance of what's occurring, and be able to make educated decisions at that point.

